Package drcl.inet.core.queue

Class Summary
DropTail  
FIFO Implements a FIFO queue structure that one may plug in a different queue logic to form a differnt FIFO implementation.
FRED The Fair Random Early Detection queue logic.
MQueue MQueue is an m-level queue generalized from RIO and 3-Color queue.
PreemptPriorityQueue PreemptPriorityQueue is the same as PriorityQueue except that an arrived higher-priority packet can preempt (and drop) a lower-priority packet when the queue is full.
PriorityQueue PriorityQueue is an m-level queue.
RED The Random Early Detection (RED) queue logic.
SRED The Stabalized Random Early Detection queue logic.
